<section style="position:relative; background:#0E2E29; color:#EAF1EE; overflow:hidden; background-image:linear-gradient(rgba(255,255,255,.04) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,rgba(255,255,255,.04) 1px,transparent 1px); background-size:46px 46px;">
  <div style="position:absolute; bottom:-20%; left:50%; transform:translateX(-50%); width:60%; height:80%; background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(230,178,58,.13),transparent 60%); pointer-events:none;"></div>
  <div style="position:relative; max-width:1120px; margin:0 auto; padding:clamp(48px,7vw,96px) clamp(24px,5vw,56px); text-align:center;">
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-head); font-weight:800; font-size:clamp(28px,5vw,56px); line-height:1.02; letter-spacing:-0.035em; margin:0 auto; max-width:20ch;">{L("Was davon klemmt bei euch gerade?", "Which of these is pinching you right now?", "眼下这些当中，哪一项正让贵厂头疼？")}</h2>
    <p style="font-size:clamp(16px,1.7vw,20px); color:#C7D8D2; max-width:52ch; margin:20px auto 30px;">{L("Schreib's roh in eine Pain-List — wir sagen dir, welche Bausteine greifen.", "Jot it raw into a pain list — we'll tell you which building blocks fit.", "把它随手写进一份痛点清单——我们会告诉您哪些模块能对症。")}</p>
