      <a href={b + "/stack/"} style="font-family:var(--font-mono); font-size:13px; color:#A6CFC5; display:inline-flex; align-items:center;">{L("So ist der Stack gebaut", "How the stack is built", "技术栈是如何构建的")} ↗</a>
